{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c6ecde95fb","title":"关于全国财政会议的议题和准备工作给陈云等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f3c61ed898","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":6,"articleId":"c6ecde95fb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"bf02d3b681","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。"},{"id":"2b3c4b4d25","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"一波，即薄一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任兼财政部部长。富春，即李富春，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任。"},{"id":"7cd72a38b7","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杨立三，当时任人民革命军事委员会总后勤部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"72cdf66364","type":"title","text":"关于全国财政会议的议题和准备工作给陈云\"等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb"},{"id":"bf02d3b681","type":"paragraph","text":"陈云、一波、富春同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb"},{"id":"2b3c4b4d25","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十日开始的财政会议，应讨论些什么问题，请你们考虑一下，并在发开会通知中写进去，使各地有所准备。似乎预算问题，增薪问题，县区乡财政统一问题，地方财政和大城市财政问题，税收问题，五年计划问题，今年下半年经济安排问题，军费问题（杨立三应参加），均应有所讨论，除由你们对每项问题准备方案外，各天区财委最好能在本月中句召开一次财政会议，收集意见带来（已开者如西南当然不要召开）。是否可行，请的定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb"},{"id":"7cd72a38b7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb"},{"id":"00d62859c4","type":"paragraph","text":"五月六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"c6ecde95fb"}],"